    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "This happens if the actor is killed in a FrameEndTask in the same frame but after the carryall pickup task has run.  Repro case:  add `self.World.AddFrameEndTask(w => cargo.Dispose());` to the bottom of `PickupUnit.Attach` and wait on the d2k shellmap.  The fix will be to check for and clean up dead carried actors in the carryall internals."
  },
